name: Riven | League of Legends
description:
LoRA trained on Riven from League of Legends

requested by @1797437344610

models used

anime: YabaL_Mix V3

2,5D: PastelDiffusedMix - V2.1, CamelliaMIx_2.5D - V2, DarkSun

realistic: Paragon V1.0

tags: riven \(league of legends\), 1girl,

optional tags: folded ponytail, short dress, corset, single pauldron, white hair, black eyeshadow, bare shoulders, facial mark

negative embeddings: bad-hands-5, ng_deepnegative_v1_75t, bad-artist, EasyNegative

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (for realistic models & 2,5D), kl-f8-anime2, blessed2.vae (for anime models)

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras or DPM++ 2M Karras(euler a for img2img upscaling)

  • Steps: 20 to 35

  • Clipskip: 2

  • Upscaler : GitHub - pkuliyi2015/multidiffusion-upscaler-for-automatic1111 4x-UltraSharp(for 2,5D & realistic), 4xAnimesharp(for anime)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9 (mostly 7)

  • LORA weight for txt2img: 0.5-1 (for the examples i mostly used 0.8)

  • Denoise strength upscaling: 0.4 to 0.7

for full body shots i recommend using: ComfyUI Impact Pack

or the a1111 alternative GitHub - Bing-su/adetailer
